title: Carl Barks Digital Archive Set 01 to 12 Retro
description:
Carl Barks Digital Archive Retro:

Un-cropped Comics!
Thanks to the original comic scanners!

Set 01 to 10 in Carl Barks Library order 
representing all the original scanned
comics that I have been collecting for years!

Bonus:

Set 11 Early Years   - Benny Burro & Barney Bear comics, etc. 
                       and NOT including the many bonus features
                       and updated scans
Set 12 Final Stories - Stories are in no particular order 
                       and NOT the final version of CBDA Set 12


Happy Holidays!
